---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="AI Solutions Across Industries | AutiMind" 
  description="Transform your industry with AutiMind's custom AI solutions. We serve Manufacturing, Healthcare, Food & Beverage, Automotive, Energy, and Defense sectors worldwide with cutting-edge artificial intelligence technology."
  keywords="AI solutions by industry, manufacturing AI, automotive AI development, food beverage AI, healthcare AI solutions, industrial AI automation, defense AI technology, energy sector AI, global AI development, enterprise AI solutions, custom AI applications, AI transformation services, intelligent automation, machine learning solutions, AI consulting services, industrial automation AI"
  canonicalUrl="https://autimind.com/industries"
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-8">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            AI Solutions
          </span>
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">Across Industries</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Transforming industries worldwide with cutting-edge AI technology. From automotive manufacturing to healthcare, we deliver custom AI solutions that drive efficiency, innovation, and growth across diverse global markets.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-16">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400">50+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400">Industries Served</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400">100+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400">AI Solutions Deployed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400">95%</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400">Client Satisfaction</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400">24/7</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400">Global Support</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Manufacturing & Automotive -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-800/30">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Manufacturing & Automotive
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
              The backbone of modern industry worldwide, from automotive giants to precision manufacturing. Our AI solutions optimize production lines, predict maintenance needs, and enhance quality control across global manufacturing networks.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Predictive Maintenance AI</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Reduce downtime and maintenance costs with AI-powered equipment monitoring</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Quality Control Automation</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Computer vision systems for real-time defect detection and quality assurance</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Supply Chain Optimization</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-driven logistics and inventory management for just-in-time manufacturing</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/20 to-cyan-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-teal-500/30">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Industry Applications</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Automotive Manufacturing</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Electronics & Semiconductors</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Aerospace & Defense</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Industrial Equipment</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Food & Beverage -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="relative order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-red-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-orange-500/30">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Global Food Innovation</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Consumer Packaged Goods</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Food Processing & Manufacturing</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Beverage Production</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Restaurant & Hospitality Chains</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-orange-500/10 rounded-lg border border-orange-500/20">
                <p class="text-sm text-orange-200">Transforming food systems with AI innovation</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-red-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Food & Beverage Industry
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
              From global food giants to emerging food tech startups, we provide AI solutions that modernize production, enhance quality control, and optimize supply chains for the next generation of food manufacturing worldwide.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Recipe Optimization AI</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-powered formulation and nutrition optimization for new products</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Food Safety Monitoring</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Real-time contamination detection and compliance automation</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Production Line Intelligence</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-driven efficiency improvements and waste reduction</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Healthcare & Social Assistance -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-800/30">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-teal-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Healthcare & Social Services
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
              From hospitals and clinics to pharmaceutical companies and medical device manufacturers, we're enhancing patient care through AI-powered diagnostics, workflow optimization, and predictive analytics for better global health outcomes.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Clinical Decision Support</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-assisted diagnosis and treatment recommendation systems</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Patient Flow Optimization</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Intelligent scheduling and resource allocation for hospitals</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Medical Imaging AI</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Advanced computer vision for radiology and pathology analysis</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500/20 to-teal-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-green-500/30">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Healthcare Transformation</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Hospital Systems & Clinics</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Pharmaceutical Companies</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Medical Device Manufacturers</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Telemedicine Platforms</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Energy & Defense -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="relative order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/20 to-blue-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/30">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Critical Infrastructure</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Renewable Energy Systems</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Defense & Aerospace</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Utilities & Smart Grid</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Electric Vehicle Infrastructure</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-lg border border-purple-500/20">
                <p class="text-sm text-purple-200">Securing the future with intelligent infrastructure</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Energy & Defense
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
              Supporting global energy transition and defense modernization with AI solutions for smart grid management, predictive maintenance, and advanced analytics for critical infrastructure worldwide.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Smart Grid AI</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Intelligent energy distribution and demand forecasting</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Defense Analytics</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Advanced data analysis and pattern recognition for defense applications</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Infrastructure Monitoring</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-powered monitoring and maintenance of critical systems</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Economic Impact -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-800/50">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Driving Global Digital Transformation
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          AutiMind is committed to supporting global economic growth and industrial innovation through AI technology that creates value, drives efficiency, and positions organizations worldwide as leaders in intelligent automation and digital transformation.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-gray-800/80 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-2">40%</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Efficiency Gains</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Average improvement with AI implementation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-800/80 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-2">85%</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Cost Reduction</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">In operational expenses through automation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-800/80 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-2">6x</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">ROI Multiplier</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Return on AI investment within 18 months</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/20 to-orange-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-teal-500/30">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Transform Your Industry?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Join global industry leaders who are already leveraging AI to drive innovation, efficiency, and sustainable growth across their organizations.
          </p>
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-orange-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:from-teal-600 hover:to-orange-600 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
            Get Started Today
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>